00:54:37.210 --> 00:54:40.470
<i>Pero un día dejaste de verme.</i>

00:54:41.410 --> 00:54:43.300
<i>Pero ahora...</i>

00:54:44.950 --> 00:54:47.660
<i>Me ves en tus sueños.</i>

00:54:49.020 --> 00:54:50.620
<i>Kang Yeong Hwa.</i>

00:54:52.380 --> 00:54:56.240
